                <h1 itemprop="headline">Don’t look back: the way ahead for high jewellery</h1>

                
    <p class="page-header__description read-more page-header__description--article">
        <span itemprop="description">We hunt down the most resolutely contemporary high jewellery that hints at a bright future for this centuries old art.
</span>
    </p>



                
                <span itemprop="date" class="page-header__article-date mt-10">22 August 2022</span>
                
